# MRARRANGER Skills System

You have access to the `mrarranger-skills` MCP server with 26 specialized skills.

## Workflow
1. When user asks anything → check if a skill matches (see routing below)
2. Call `search_skills` or `list_skills` MCP tool to find the right skill
3. Call `load_skill` to get full instructions
4. Call `load_reference` for specific sub-skill details
5. Follow loaded instructions precisely

